snippet.title: void* tRrLM2(); //Void Terrarium 2 - Launch Trailer (Nintendo Switch, PS4)
snippet.description:
Out Now!
Learn more @ https://nisamerica.com/void-terrarium/2

The future is rooted in the past. In Void Terrarium 2, your mission to protect the last living human continues. Explore the toxic wasteland for critical supplies while exploring visions of the past in order to save the present. Then return to your terrarium safe zone to nurture and care for Toriko, the last living human, by curing her illnesses, maintaining and decorating the terrarium, and even dressing her up and playing games.

Available now on Nintendo Switch and PS4!

#VoidTerrarium2
